      <hedline>
        <hl1>COMPANY BRIEFS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Bristol-Myers Squibb will acquire Redmond Products Inc for undisclosed terms (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>BRISTOL-MYERS SQUIBB, New York, the pharmaceutical company, will acquire Redmond Products Inc., a privately held hair-care company, for undisclosed terms.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>BRISTOL-MYERS SQUIBB, New York, the pharmaceutical company, will acquire Redmond Products Inc., a privately held hair-care company, for undisclosed terms.</p>
        <p>DEAN FOODS CO., Franklin Park, Ill., the dairy processor and distributor, said it had agreed to buy Penn Traffic Co.'s Sani-Dairy milk unit for $37.5 million in cash.</p>
        <p>FIFTH THIRD BANCORP, Cincinnati, agreed to buy Ohio Co. for an undisclosed amount, as the bank expands its asset management and begins equity and debt underwriting.</p>
      </block>
